cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "fatigue-tree2: Probabilistic Eccentric Decay Geometry Monte Carlo for Wind-Fatigue of Urban Street Trees"
message: "If you use this software or data, please cite the accompanying paper and this archive."
type: software
