repository-code: "https://github.com/windkplus/fatigue-tree2"
url: "https://github.com/windkplus/fatigue-tree2"
abstract: >-
  Closed-form eccentric / elliptical cavity stress-amplification framework
  with Monte Carlo confidence intervals on wind-induced fatigue life of
  urban street trees, validated against ABAQUS Standard 2026. Companion
  to the deterministic concentric-decay framework of Kang (2026), Trees -
  Structure and Function (Paper I).
keywords:
  - wind-fatigue
  - eccentric decay
  - Monte Carlo
  - urban street trees
  - probabilistic risk assessment
  - sonic tomography
  - ABAQUS validation
